############
data2wav:	convert message data into .wav file										@48kHz

Transmitter_V0.1:	send message/command in txt file repeatly untill stop			@48kHz
Transmitter_V1.1:	send message/command written in terminal repeatly untill stop	@48kHz
Receiver_V0.1:	receive message/command and print on terminal and append to file	@48kHz
Receiver_V1.1:	P_receive message/command and print on terminal and append to file	@48kHz

# m = 2, BW: 400 Hz, Fc: 19kHz
# Packet initial alignment
# CPFSK zero crossing based receiver
# No passive topology
# vol -> 100%
# Sensitivity AGC
# LOS matter


